data.description: Step into style and comfort in this gem! The open floor plan flows from the huge living room to the upgraded kitchen with beautiful Maple cabinets and tile backsplash. Open up the stunning French doors to the huge private formal dinning room. Enjoy a private large fenced-in yard and the convenience of a huge two-car attached garage. Located in the Highland Rim school district! Make it yours and start creating memories in a home that effortlessly combines elegance and functionality. Welcome to your dream home!
